635 static void* get_proc(const char *namez);
636 
637 #if defined(_WIN32) || defined(__CYGWIN__)
638 #ifndef _WINDOWS_
639 #undef APIENTRY
640 #endif
641 #include <windows.h>
642 static HMODULE libGL;
643 
644 typedef void* (APIENTRYP PFNWGLGETPROCADDRESSPROC_PRIVATE)(const char*);
645 static PFNWGLGETPROCADDRESSPROC_PRIVATE gladGetProcAddressPtr;
646 
647 #ifdef _MSC_VER
648 #ifdef __has_include
649  #if __has_include(<winapifamily.h>)
650  #define HAVE_WINAPIFAMILY 1
651  #endif
652 #elif _MSC_VER >= 1700 && !_USING_V110_SDK71_
653  #define HAVE_WINAPIFAMILY 1
654 #endif
655 #endif
656 
657 #ifdef HAVE_WINAPIFAMILY
658  #include <winapifamily.h>
659  #if !WINAPI_FAMILY_PARTITION(WINAPI_PARTITION_DESKTOP) && WINAPI_FAMILY_PARTITION(WINAPI_PARTITION_APP)
660  #define IS_UWP 1
661  #endif
662 #endif
663 
664 static
665 int open_gl(void) {
666 #ifndef IS_UWP
667  libGL = LoadLibraryW(L"opengl32.dll");
668  if(libGL != NULL) {
669  void (* tmp)(void);
670  tmp = (void(*)(void)) GetProcAddress(libGL, "wglGetProcAddress");
671  gladGetProcAddressPtr = (PFNWGLGETPROCADDRESSPROC_PRIVATE) tmp;
672  return gladGetProcAddressPtr != NULL;
673  }
674 #endif
675 
676  return 0;
677 }
678 
679 static
680 void close_gl(void) {
681  if(libGL != NULL) {
682  FreeLibrary((HMODULE) libGL);
683  libGL = NULL;
684  }
685 }
686 #else
687 #include <dlfcn.h>
688 static void* libGL;
689 
690 #if !defined(__APPLE__) && !defined(__HAIKU__)
691 typedef void* (APIENTRYP PFNGLXGETPROCADDRESSPROC_PRIVATE)(const char*);
692 static PFNGLXGETPROCADDRESSPROC_PRIVATE gladGetProcAddressPtr;
693 #endif
694 
695 static
696 int open_gl(void) {
697 #ifdef __APPLE__
698  static const char *NAMES[] = {
699  "../Frameworks/OpenGL.framework/OpenGL",
700  "/Library/Frameworks/OpenGL.framework/OpenGL",
701  "/System/Library/Frameworks/OpenGL.framework/OpenGL",
702  "/System/Library/Frameworks/OpenGL.framework/Versions/Current/OpenGL"
703  };
704 #else
705  static const char *NAMES[] = {"libGL.so.1", "libGL.so"};
706 #endif
707 
708  unsigned int index = 0;
709  for(index = 0; index < (sizeof(NAMES) / sizeof(NAMES[0])); index++) {
710  libGL = dlopen(NAMES[index], RTLD_NOW | RTLD_GLOBAL);
711 
712  if(libGL != NULL) {
713 #if defined(__APPLE__) || defined(__HAIKU__)
714  return 1;
715 #else
716  gladGetProcAddressPtr = (PFNGLXGETPROCADDRESSPROC_PRIVATE)dlsym(libGL,
717  "glXGetProcAddressARB");
718  return gladGetProcAddressPtr != NULL;
719 #endif
720  }
721  }
722 
723  return 0;
724 }
725 
726 static
727 void close_gl(void) {
728  if(libGL != NULL) {
729  dlclose(libGL);
730  libGL = NULL;
731  }
732 }
733 #endif
734 
735 static
736 void* get_proc(const char *namez) {
737  void* result = NULL;
738  if(libGL == NULL) return NULL;
739 
740 #if !defined(__APPLE__) && !defined(__HAIKU__)
741  if(gladGetProcAddressPtr != NULL) {
742  result = gladGetProcAddressPtr(namez);
743  }
744 #endif
745  if(result == NULL) {
746 #if defined(_WIN32) || defined(__CYGWIN__)
747  result = (void*)GetProcAddress((HMODULE) libGL, namez);
748 #else
749  result = dlsym(libGL, namez);
750 #endif
751  }
752 
753  return result;
754 }
755 
756 int gladLoadGL(void) {
757  int status = 0;
758 
759  if(open_gl()) {
760  status = gladLoadGLLoader(&get_proc);
761  close_gl();
762  }
763 
764  return status;
765 }
766 
767 struct gladGLversionStruct GLVersion = { 0, 0 };
768 
769 #if defined(GL_ES_VERSION_3_0) || defined(GL_VERSION_3_0)
770 #define _GLAD_IS_SOME_NEW_VERSION 1
771 #endif
772 
773 static int max_loaded_major;
774 static int max_loaded_minor;
775 
776 static const char *exts = NULL;
777 static int num_exts_i = 0;
778 static char **exts_i = NULL;
779 
780 static int get_exts(void) {
781 #ifdef _GLAD_IS_SOME_NEW_VERSION
782  if(max_loaded_major < 3) {
783 #endif
784  exts = (const char *)glGetString(GL_EXTENSIONS);
785 #ifdef _GLAD_IS_SOME_NEW_VERSION
786  } else {
787  unsigned int index;
788 
789  num_exts_i = 0;
790  glGetIntegerv(GL_NUM_EXTENSIONS, &num_exts_i);
791  if (num_exts_i > 0) {
792  exts_i = (char **)malloc((size_t)num_exts_i * (sizeof *exts_i));
793  }
794 
795  if (exts_i == NULL) {
796  return 0;
797  }
798 
799  for(index = 0; index < (unsigned)num_exts_i; index++) {
800  const char *gl_str_tmp = (const char*)glGetStringi(GL_EXTENSIONS, index);
801  size_t len = strlen(gl_str_tmp);
802 
803  char *local_str = (char*)malloc((len+1) * sizeof(char));
804  if(local_str != NULL) {
805  memcpy(local_str, gl_str_tmp, (len+1) * sizeof(char));
806  }
807  exts_i[index] = local_str;
808  }
809  }
810 #endif
811  return 1;
812 }
813 
814 static void free_exts(void) {
815  if (exts_i != NULL) {
816  int index;
817  for(index = 0; index < num_exts_i; index++) {
818  free((char *)exts_i[index]);
819  }
820  free((void *)exts_i);
821  exts_i = NULL;
822  }
823 }
824 
825 static int has_ext(const char *ext) {
826 #ifdef _GLAD_IS_SOME_NEW_VERSION
827  if(max_loaded_major < 3) {
828 #endif
829  const char *extensions;
830  const char *loc;
831  const char *terminator;
832  extensions = exts;
833  if(extensions == NULL || ext == NULL) {
834  return 0;
835  }
836 
837  while(1) {
838  loc = strstr(extensions, ext);
839  if(loc == NULL) {
840  return 0;
841  }
842 
843  terminator = loc + strlen(ext);
844  if((loc == extensions || *(loc - 1) == ' ') &&
845  (*terminator == ' ' || *terminator == '\0')) {
846  return 1;
847  }
848  extensions = terminator;
849  }
850 #ifdef _GLAD_IS_SOME_NEW_VERSION
851  } else {
852  int index;
853  if(exts_i == NULL) return 0;
854  for(index = 0; index < num_exts_i; index++) {
855  const char *e = exts_i[index];
856 
857  if(exts_i[index] != NULL && strcmp(e, ext) == 0) {
858  return 1;
859  }
860  }
861  }
862 #endif
863 
864  return 0;
865 }

9641 
9642 static void find_coreGL(void) {
9643 
9644  /* Thank you @elmindreda
9645  * https://github.com/elmindreda/greg/blob/master/templates/greg.c.in#L176
9646  * https://github.com/glfw/glfw/blob/master/src/context.c#L36
9647  */
9648  int i, major, minor;
9649 
9650  const char* version;
9651  const char* prefixes[] = {
9652  "OpenGL ES-CM ",
9653  "OpenGL ES-CL ",
9654  "OpenGL ES ",
9655  NULL
9656  };
9657 
9658  version = (const char*) glGetString(GL_VERSION);
9659  if (!version) return;
9660 
9661  for (i = 0; prefixes[i]; i++) {
9662  const size_t length = strlen(prefixes[i]);
9663  if (strncmp(version, prefixes[i], length) == 0) {
9664  version += length;
9665  break;
9666  }
9667  }
9668 
9669 /* PR #18 */
9670 #ifdef _MSC_VER
9671  sscanf_s(version, "%d.%d", &major, &minor);
9672 #else
9673  sscanf(version, "%d.%d", &major, &minor);
9674 #endif
9675 
9676  GLVersion.major = major; GLVersion.minor = minor;
9677  max_loaded_major = major; max_loaded_minor = minor;
9678  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_0 = (major == 1 && minor >= 0) || major > 1;
9679  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_1 = (major == 1 && minor >= 1) || major > 1;
9680  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_2 = (major == 1 && minor >= 2) || major > 1;
9681  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_3 = (major == 1 && minor >= 3) || major > 1;
9682  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_4 = (major == 1 && minor >= 4) || major > 1;
9683  GLAD_GL_VERSION_1_5 = (major == 1 && minor >= 5) || major > 1;
9684  GLAD_GL_VERSION_2_0 = (major == 2 && minor >= 0) || major > 2;
9685  GLAD_GL_VERSION_2_1 = (major == 2 && minor >= 1) || major > 2;
9686  GLAD_GL_VERSION_3_0 = (major == 3 && minor >= 0) || major > 3;
9687  GLAD_GL_VERSION_3_1 = (major == 3 && minor >= 1) || major > 3;
9688  GLAD_GL_VERSION_3_2 = (major == 3 && minor >= 2) || major > 3;
9689  GLAD_GL_VERSION_3_3 = (major == 3 && minor >= 3) || major > 3;
9690  GLAD_GL_VERSION_4_0 = (major == 4 && minor >= 0) || major > 4;
9691  GLAD_GL_VERSION_4_1 = (major == 4 && minor >= 1) || major > 4;
9692  GLAD_GL_VERSION_4_2 = (major == 4 && minor >= 2) || major > 4;
9693  GLAD_GL_VERSION_4_3 = (major == 4 && minor >= 3) || major > 4;
9694  GLAD_GL_VERSION_4_4 = (major == 4 && minor >= 4) || major > 4;
9695  GLAD_GL_VERSION_4_5 = (major == 4 && minor >= 5) || major > 4;
9696  GLAD_GL_VERSION_4_6 = (major == 4 && minor >= 6) || major > 4;
9697  if (GLVersion.major > 4 || (GLVersion.major >= 4 && GLVersion.minor >= 6)) {
9698  max_loaded_major = 4;
9699  max_loaded_minor = 6;
9700  }
9701 }
